Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph <chapter-uri>/title set

Purpose:
  Rename an existing chapter in the archive TOC.

Usage:
  wikigraph <chapter-uri>/title set <title> [--llm <json>] [--help|-h]
  wikigraph <chapter-uri>/title clear [--llm <json>] [--help|-h]

Behavior:
  - Updates only the chapter title stored in the TOC.
  - Does not change source text, graph nodes, summaries, or metadata.
  - `set <title>` sets the explicit title.
  - `clear` removes the explicit title and shows `[untitled]`.
  - Does not call an LLM provider.

Output shape:
  Prints the updated chapter object.

Examples:
  wikigraph wkg://book.wikg/chapter/12/title set "New Chapter Title"
  wikigraph wkg://book.wikg/chapter/12/title clear

See also:
  - wikigraph wkg://book.wikg/chapter list --help
  - wikigraph wkg://book.wikg/chapter/12/state get --help
  - wikigraph help command
